              fieldset.form-group
                label(for='exampleInputEmail1') Get early access!
                input#userEmail.form-control(type='email', placeholder='email')
              button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Get App
    .fit-section-white
        .container
          .row
            h3.text-xs-center How it works
